She looked at RatTrap with suprize.  She wasn't expecting a bot to 
just come out of the forest like that.  She pulled out her 
dagger, "Who are you?" She looked for a symbol to identify him with.

wrote:
> Rattrap:
> 
>

used to

But 
> what? The only bots that he ever came in contact with were the ones 
that

him.

finally 
> made it out of the forest. He looked behind himself and watched the 
skies 
> for the Predacon fliers. That was when he bumped into something
